snippet.textDisplay:
The keerthanam just blew me off! Hats off to Shriram Iyer!
Meaning:
There is no other (“vere”) deity (“daivam”) equal (“samana”) to Nataraja, the lord (“pathi”) of the stage (“sabha”). In this world (“bhoomi thannil”), you cannot find a kinder deity (“kripanidhi”) than him (“ivaraipolai”).
